superMiscConds.notes:
No contact with the victim or the victims family;
No contact with juveniles under the age of 18 without prior agent approval;
Submit a DNA sample and pay costs for same;
Pay court costs;
Complete a sex offender assessment and follow through with the recommended treatment and aftercare;
Cooperate with and complete programming deemed necessary by the Department of Corrections; 
Comply with Wisconsin Sex Offender Registry Program;
Comply with a mental health treatment and take all prescribed medications.
